4F1GY0%2Bs36xT1iXQeKYI0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=3e2245dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tYBl9jhuDvo</a><br />\n<br />\nbackup佬琴日話問過達哥但達哥無覆。而佢都自動停左做backup。<br />\no係度我希望達哥認真覆一覆佢(甚至係其他精華兄弟)。如果你真係唔鍾意,介意佢地影響你收入或者乜乜物物都好,同佢地禮貌講聲,所有野你自己做返,我諗係最好既結果。但如果連覆都唔覆,甚至想怪咁多位backup同精華兄弟,我會對你好失望...﻿<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;&lt;留言位人兄已經刪除留言</span><br />\n<br />\n早排先係fifa度暗示過youtube有人偷片揾食唔問佢，而家達太祖立刻宣示主權！！ 不過冇chatroom版我都係會睇番backup佬<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmXtR8ghgHJbahuBVnZkBDZ2kG2fbUjXvf7hVCvmKF71c4?filename=1cQtdLa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1cQtdLa.png&h=b80d6cba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n每次達哥玩人中，兄弟都唔洗睇chatroom，全部都係劇透，嗌skip劇情，好慢好悶呢啲comment﻿<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/21/235611_56ddc46eae1a162892c6a8c490cfb3a0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F21%2F235611_56ddc46eae1a162892c6a8c490cfb3a0.png&h=a26ed78e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實唔可以咁講, 只係一開始undergrounddv自己唔放上youtube, youtube佬只係幫大家放上另一個渠道加chatroom俾大家重溫, 大膽d講, 呢幾年無左backup佬, 會有咁多人睇達哥？backup佬無功都有勞, 同埋宣示主權既概念唔係好岩, 達哥somehow都係攞人地隻game搵食, 開發商大可以用同一個道理唔俾達哥用佢隻game, 大家彼此留個空間比較好, 支持backup佬繼續雙版本backup~﻿<br />\n<br />\ntwitch download唔到, Youtube可以, download定出街唁洗數據都睇到﻿<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaXUSmTkpP8RNBYZkdaytHrSGfwxDLSvBKF7Ght5zRhGf?filename=548o32z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F548o32z.png&h=af0c6f95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\ninclude埋chatroom先會睇呢邊﻿<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfN3Y3oy2fiNa4bYj73tyDoWLtER8o6zN7MXSpbT1ZdSP?filename=WSUdDd0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWSUdDd0.png&h=89636a8d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"90a1cea2c8433f62be0dc29b9c70e5a319c6644a","tid":89780,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T16:59:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主好有心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前有幾個留言就咁copy and paste偷片撚fb youtube del咗嘅留言，無寫明quote，或者花時間cap圖cut咗啲無辜嘅人，而家有幾條友當我幾日前覺得達哥忘恩負義"},{"pid":"197a9001d0f95368dc4bde2d5d6a32dc59057bda","tid":89780,"uid":77685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T00:31:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主好有心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我之前有幾個留言就咁copy and paste偷片撚fb youtube del咗嘅留言，無寫明quote，或者花時間cap圖cut咗啲無辜嘅人，而家有幾條友當我幾日前覺得達哥忘恩負義</blockquote><br />\n我信你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}